[% PROCESS "global/variables.none.tmpl" %]
From: [% Param('mailfrom') %]
To: [% to_user.email %]
Subject: [[% terms.Bug %] [%+ bugid %]] [% 'Nový: ' IF isnew %][%+ summary %]
X-Bugzilla-Reason: [% reasonsheader %]
X-Bugzilla-Type: [% isnew ? 'new' : 'changed' %]
X-Bugzilla-Watch-Reason: [% reasonswatchheader %]
[% IF Param('useclassification') %]
X-Bugzilla-Classification: [% classification %]
[% END %]
X-Bugzilla-Product: [% product %]
X-Bugzilla-Component: [% comp %]
X-Bugzilla-Keywords: [% keywords %]
X-Bugzilla-Severity: [% severity %]
X-Bugzilla-Who: [% changer %]
X-Bugzilla-Status: [% status %]
X-Bugzilla-Priority: [% priority %]
X-Bugzilla-Assigned-To: [% assignedto %]
X-Bugzilla-Target-Milestone: [% targetmilestone %]
X-Bugzilla-Changed-Fields: [% changedfields %]
[%+ threadingmarker %]

[% FOREACH comment = new_comments %]

[%- IF comment.count %]
--- Komentář #[% comment.count %] od [% comment.author.identity %] [%+ comment.time FILTER time(undef, to_user.timezone) %] ---
[% END %]
[%+ comment.body_full({ is_bugmail => 1, wrap => 1 }) %]
[% END %]

[%+ urlbase %]show_bug.cgi?id=[% bugid %]
[%- IF diffs %]

[%+ diffs %]
[% END -%]

-- [%# Protect the trailing space of the signature marker %]
Konfigurace zpráv: [% urlbase %]userprefs.cgi?tab=email
------- Tento email jste přijal z tohoto důvodu: -------
[% FOREACH relationship = reasons %]
  [% SWITCH relationship %]
    [% CASE constants.REL_ASSIGNEE %]
Jset uveden jako příjemce [% terms.bug2 %].
    [% CASE constants.REL_REPORTER %]
Nahlásil jste tento [% terms.bug %].
    [% CASE constants.REL_QA %]
Jste QA kontakt pro tento [% terms.bug %].
    [% CASE constants.REL_CC %]
Jste uveden v seznamu do Kopie tohoto [% terms.bug2 %].
    [% CASE constants.REL_VOTER %]
Dal jste hlas tomuto[% terms.bug2 %].
    [% CASE constants.REL_GLOBAL_WATCHER %]
Sledujete všechny změny [% terms.bugsu %].
  [% END %]
[% END %]
[% FOREACH relationship = reasons_watch %]
  [% SWITCH relationship %]
    [% CASE constants.REL_ASSIGNEE %]
Sledujete příjemce tohoto [% terms.bug2 %].
    [% CASE constants.REL_REPORTER %]
Sledujete toho kdo nahlásil tento [% terms.bug %].
    [% CASE constants.REL_QA %]
Sledujete toho QA kontakt tohoto [% terms.bug2 %].
    [% CASE constants.REL_CC %]
Sledujete někoho kdo je uveden v kopii tohoto [% terms.bug2 %].
    [% CASE constants.REL_VOTER %]
Sledujete někoho kdo dal hlas tomuto [% terms.bug2 %].
  [% END %]
[% END %]
